          "date": "2022-05-20 15:54:52.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-15878 contrib: add lustre_opcode",
        "message": "LU-15878 contrib: add lustre_opcode\n\nAdd a Lustre RPC opcode encoder/decoder to contrib/scripts/.\n\n$ lustre_opcode 101\n 101 LDLM_ENQUEUE\n$ lustre_opcode LDLM_ENQUEUE\n 101 LDLM_ENQUEUE\n$ lustre_opcode enq\n 101 LDLM_ENQUEUE\n$ lustre_opcode GETA\n  1 OST_GETATTR\n 33 MDS_GETATTR\n 34 MDS_GETATTR_NAME\n$ lustre_opcode FLD\n 900 FLD_QUERY\n 901 FLD_READ\n$ lustre_opcode OUT\n  61 MDS_SWAP_LAYOUTS\n1000 OUT_UPDATE\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <jhammond@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I6af73094f6b2c84b9a973e259c316d29af8d55d6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
